# Guide Page Sync

`src/pages/GuidePage.tsx` documents how to use the app. When you modify any feature covered by the guide, check whether the guide text still accurately describes the current behavior.

## Rules

- After changing import, export, AI tailoring, preview, form sections, or PWA install behavior, read the relevant section in `GuidePage.tsx` and update it if the description no longer matches.
- Do not add or remove guide sections without explicit user confirmation.
- Keep guide text concise and factual — no marketing language.
- If you rename a UI element (button label, section title, etc.) that the guide references by name, update the guide to match.
- Screenshot placeholder slots (`ScreenshotSlot`) should not be removed or reordered without asking.
